OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784810903
OL,3,CThames Water announces hosepipe ban
OL,4,Cfor millions of customers
OL,6,FThames Water has announced a hosepipe
OL,7,Fban for just over 10 million customers
OL,8,Fas the exceptionally dry, hot weather
OL,9,Fdrives a surge in demand.
OL,11,FThe restriction, also known as a
OL,12,Ftemporary use ban (TUB), will come
OL,13,Finto effect at 12.01am on Thursday.
OL,15,FBut the utility is also asking
OL,16,Fhouseholds to follow the ban
OL,17,Fimmediately, ahead of its official
OL,18,Fstart date.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
