FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784810903
OL,3,CThames Water announces hosepipe ban
OL,4,Cfor millions of customers
OL,6,FRainfall totals for the month of July
OL,7,Fto date ranged from 9% of the long-
OL,8,Fterm average in north-west England to
OL,9,Fnothing in east and south-east
OL,10,FEngland, the Met Office said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
